description:
FASTQ files for Mpox genomic sequences, generated by tiled-amplicon PCR amplification and Nanopore MinION DNA sequencing. Used to generate MPXV-USA-IL-IDPH-001 through MPXV-USA-IL-IDPH-084 consensus sequences, accessible on NCBI Genbank. 

